        "main": true,
        "title": "Etherfi - Crypto Staking Platform | Ether FI",
        "meta_descr": "Ether.fi is a decentralized liquid restaking protocol on Ethereum that lets users stake ETH, earn rewards, and maintain liquidity through eETH while retaining control of their assets.",
